OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784832502
OL,3,CFire breaks out at school in Port
OL,4,CTalbot with children and staff
OL,5,Cevacuated
OL,7,FA fire has broken out at a school in
OL,8,FPort Talbot with children and staff
OL,9,Fhaving to be evacuated to safety
OL,11,FAlthough the main school is now closed
OL,12,Fto pupils for the summer holidays, the
OL,13,Fnursery group at Awel Y Mor was still
OL,14,Fin session when the fire took place.
OL,16,F'Lots of Tots' playgroup has confirmed
OL,17,Fthat all staff and children are safe.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
