OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784832502
OL,3,CFire breaks out at school in Port
OL,4,CTalbot with children and staff
OL,5,Cevacuated
OL,7,FImages and videos on local social
OL,8,Fmedia groups show large flames and
OL,9,Fsmoke coming from the building. Other
OL,10,Fvideos show fire crews in attendance
OL,11,Fat the scene.
OL,13,FMid & West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService confirmed that the fire began
OL,15,Fwithin sandwich panels of the school.
OL,17,FIn a post on Facebook the nursery
OL,18,Fposted: ''Following the fire in the
OL,19,Fmain school building, we'll remain
OL,20,Fclosed for the rest of this week.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
