PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784832502
OL,3,CFire breaks out at school in Port
OL,4,CTalbot with children and staff
OL,5,Cevacuated
OL,7,F"We'll assess the damage and plan for
OL,8,Fthe safe return of children and staff
OL,9,Fto the undamaged playgroup. A
OL,10,Freopening date or decision can't be
OL,11,Fmade until a full assessment is
OL,12,Fcomplete.
OL,14,F"Finally, a massive thank you to the
OL,15,Fstaff for their calm and professional
OL,16,Fevacuation of the children and
OL,17,Fensuring everyone's safety.''
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
