PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784832502
OL,3,CFire breaks out at school in Port
OL,4,CTalbot with children and staff
OL,5,Cevacuated
OL,7,FIn a statement Mid and West Wales Fire
OL,8,Fand Rescue Service said, ''At 10:10am
OL,9,Fon Wednesday 22nd July, crews from
OL,10,FPort Talbot, Neath Swansea Central,
OL,11,FMorriston and Swansea West Fire
OL,12,FStations were called to an incident at
OL,13,FAwel Y Mor Primary School, Port Talbot.
OL,15,F"..Crews utilised four Breathing
OL,16,FApparatus sets and two Hose Reel Jets,
OL,17,FTurntable Ladder and Water Bowser to
OL,18,Fextinguish the fire. Crews left the
OL,19,Fscene at 12:43pm.''
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
